<p>Interesting, but the format is perhaps a bit underutilized. I liked the idea of Prometheus engaging in medical, humanitarian work as a prerequisite for the major moneymaking op, but I'm not sure a lot of the story's capacity for paratech intrigue came through, so much of it ends up being fairly dry.</p>
