<p>I have an inherent issue with the Prometheus Labs format in that my attention span and patience for scientific documents is supremely low, which isn't a particular fault of your article. But I think there's so much talk about the issue and Prometheus dragging it on that it becomes real boring to read before we even get to the Business Case. It doesn't really recover from there, in my opinion.</p>

